WEBVTT

22:09.578 --> 22:11.246
I got a deal for you.

22:15.209 --> 22:18.253
When I needed your ass,
you were nowhere to be found.

22:19.922 --> 22:22.215
Now you're trying to
hand out deals?

22:25.302 --> 22:27.512
I need you to come to Miami
and drive with me.

22:27.596 --> 22:30.974
If you do, they'll take off
that anklet and they'll
clear your entire record.

22:31.058 --> 22:33.184
I did three years in jail.

22:34.061 --> 22:35.979
Three years in jail
over you, Brian.

22:36.981 --> 22:38.523
I know you
better than you think.

22:38.607 --> 22:41.443
Maybe you don't.

22:42.319 --> 22:43.862
You guys finished?

22:44.655 --> 22:46.281
This deal legit?

22:46.907 --> 22:49.409
That's right.
If you do this job for us.

22:49.785 --> 22:50.994
I told you.

22:51.078 --> 22:52.412
Shut up, punk.

22:53.873 --> 22:55.790
So you're gonna
clean my record

22:55.875 --> 22:57.667
and get this thing
off my ankle.

22:57.752 --> 22:59.044
That's right.

22:59.628 --> 23:02.881
I thought you couldn't wander
more than 100 yards
from your home.
